      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>The collection consists chiefly of sermons by Stocker
         arranged according to the church year.</p>
         <p>The collection also contains some religious and travel
         articles by him, including articles for 
         <title render="italic">The Moravian</title>; his book reviews
         of Harry Emerson Fosdick's 
         <title render="italic">Adventurous Religion</title>and Samuel
         M. Shoemaker's 
         <title render="italic">Children of the Second Birth</title>;
         and "A Short History of the International Order of the King's
         Daughters and Sons 1886-1924" by Clara Morehouse.</p>
      </scopecontent>
